gomodel:SYNGO_4746  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Mass-spectrometric analyses of striatal synaptic vesicles of TKO versus α/γ-synuclein null mutant and WT mice contained 83 proteins (Table 1 and Fig. S3). Here, AP1B1 was detected in all experimental conditions and differentially expressed.. Experimental description: M&M: \"Generation of α-synuclein KO (from original mouse line described (30)), β-synuclein KO (from original mouse line described (49)), γ-synuclein KO (50), and α/γ-synuclein double KO mice on C57Bl6J (Charles River) background was described previously (12, 25).\"" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-4973-5732" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2286-1587" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2514-0216" ;
        dc:date           "2022-08-03" ;
